  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Rifling Trunks
---
The saying goes, "The fish should not be taken from the deep pool; the
sharp weapons of the state should not be shown to men." The sage is
the sharp weapon of the world, and therefore he should not be where the
world can see him.
